leve.name: Wrong and Rite
leve.description: A group of Sahagin has come ashore in the cover of night, and a fell ritual is underway as we speak among the tall grass of Idle Hearts. We fear they mean to strike the aetheryte at the Moraby Drydocks by employing earth magicks. In the name of the Maelstrom, end these meddlers and bury their shells where they fall.
